                                        </p>

                                    </div>

                                </div>

                                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-7 mt-6">

                                    Welcome! We are committed to providing exceptional hospitality
                                    and ensuring every guest has a comfortable and memorable stay.
                                    Feel free to contact us anytime during your visit.

                                </p>

                            </section>

                        </div>

                        <!-- Right Booking Card -->

                        <div>

                            <!-- Booking Card -->

                            <div>

                                <div class="sticky top-24 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl p-8">

